Key Match Events: Son Heung-Min scored a penalty in the 11th minute
Son Heung-Min scored a header in the final minute of the first half
Jung Seung-hyun headed a free kick from Son Heung-Min in the 87th minute
Miscellaneous Highlights: The game was played in Kuwait due to the Israel-Hamas war
Australia is top of Group I with six points
Others: Japan, Australia, Qatar, United Arab Emirates and Saudi Arabia all won
Kuwait and North Korea scored a flurry of goals en route to victories
Uzbekistan fought back from a two-goal half-time deficit to draw 2-2 with Iran
Iraq won with a 1-0 victory over hosts Vietnam
Yemen picked up their first victory in Group H with a 2-0 win over Nepal
Vietnam remain in second in the group standings after the Philippines and Indonesia shared a 1-1 draw in Manila
North Korea picked up their first win of the campaign with a 6-1 thrashing of Myanmar
Tajikistan also won 6-1 with Amadoni Kamolov hitting a brace in their victory over Pakistan in Group G
Saudi Arabia's Saleh Al Shehri scored twice in a 2-0 win over Jordan
Hong Kong twice came back from behind to draw 2-2 with Turkmenistan
Also maintaining a perfect record in Group H were United Arab Emirates with a 2-0 victory over Bahrain
Kuwait trounced Afghanistan 4-0 away to move into second place in Group A behind Qatar
The qualifying games will resume in March next year
